title: Arbor Skateboards :: 2015 Product Profiles - Oso
description:
The bear is back and stronger than ever. A throwback pool board, with a blunt nose and classic kicktail, the Oso shines on sharp transitions, barriers, and around town cruising. The Oso is dedicated to all the 70’s and 80’s bowl riders whose shoulders we stand on.

L: 31.00” W: 10.25” WB: 16.625”
